### Get all strategic decisions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions

# ============================================================================
# SEARCHS
# ============================================================================

### Search by description (default)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?q=first

### Search by description (explicit)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?q=first&by=description

### Search by topic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?q=Gastronomy&by=topic

### Search by start date - exact (specific day)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?date=2026-03-03&type=exact

### Search by start date - after (from that date onwards)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?date=2026-01-01&type=after

### Search by start date - before (until that date)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?date=2026-12-31&type=before

### Search by start date - between (range between two dates)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?date=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-06-30&type=between

### Search by end date - exact
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?date=2026-04-05&type=exact&dateField=endDate

### Search by end date - after
GET http://localhost:3000/api/decisions/search?date=2026-03-01&type=after&dateField=endDate

